{"tid":1276783,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"目標一致 要校長譚永遠收皮","createTime":"2019-07-02T04:52:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T08:16:38.000Z","uid":224260,"like":63,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"e2ae8d7b41ef477c9a0cc38ecce33b002e0068b4","tid":1276783,"uid":224260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:52:22.000Z","msg":"1.  停止購買CD 黑膠<br />\n2. 停止光顧其下餐廳 及 好友生意<br />\n3. 低價出售CD 及低價購入 <br />\n     千祈吳好剪CD<br />\n4.  大量share開心連結<br />\n     不入場購票包括電影<br />\n5. 其代言產品不作購買<br />\n<br />\n第一個 目標<br />\n校長譚<br />\n<br />\n成隊溫拿<br />\n<br />\n譚詠麟：主音歌手<br />\n鍾鎮濤：主音歌手 &amp; 和弦結他手<br />\n彭健新：結他手<br />\n葉智強：低音結他手<br />\n陳友：鼓手<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">家人資料</span>不要公開<br />\n發夢另計"},{"pid":"eab450df074ce4d2afaaf63b30ae144f393a1c98","tid":1276783,"uid":156623,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:54:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac86099851eb6bb37f9ec5543540835dcde7fbeb","tid":1276783,"uid":94824,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:55:00.000Z","msg":"校你老母"},{"pid":"09ac712fe13b7864c4759ae249c34d2807a10e77","tid":1276783,"uid":85774,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:01:24.000Z","msg":"譚伯食屎啦"},{"pid":"935b8da4984b31e5121b2e3223e1fb65272a9157","tid":1276783,"uid":243255,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:26:26.000Z","msg":"重申多一百次<br />\n<br />\n唔好再叫條友做校長<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">佢係樂壇做過D乜咁巴閉個朵要叫校長?<br />\n</span><br />\n譚伯就譚伯啦<br />\n<strong>即係廢老一名</strong><br />\n<br />\n呼籲身邊人唔好撚再食華星 &amp; 左倫右李<br />\n如果父母係藍絲 就話佢知間野唔好食<br />\n一傳10 <br />\n10傳百<br />\n<br />\n等譚老坑為自己言語付下責任! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"313783186aa76886d1b90bc4a9dd1b4a1b44123e","tid":1276783,"uid":16620,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:33:23.000